=Description=

"This is a group for people who are highly interested in and open to, or who already are convinced of, the desirability of creating new organizations to pursue the aims and logic of participatory society vision throughout society. 

The group is not itself an organization. Rather it is a vehicle to explore ideas and proposals and even on going practices by local efforts embarked on organization building, all in hopes of widespread results, in the future. The links include some to local efforts already under way to create what can become chapters of the larger, ultimately sought after, international, built on national, built on local, organizations."
(http://www.zcommunications.org/zspace/groups/people-for-an-iops)


